Oracle Cloud Free Tier er OCPU (Oracle CPU) hishab ta ami clear kore dicchi:

‚ö° Oracle Free Tier e OCPU Limit
Always Free VM.Standard.A1.Flex (ARM Ampere CPU):

4 OCPU total free (joto instance khulo, combined limit 4 OCPU).

24 GB RAM total free.

Tumi ichcha korle ekta boro VM (4 OCPU, 24GB RAM) khulte paro,
ba multiple chhoto VM (example: 2 OCPU + 12GB RAM, 1 OCPU + 6GB RAM, etc.) khulte paro.

Paid/Upgraded account hole:

Tumi instance shape change kore unlimited OCPU nite parbe (limit depend kore subscription + region quota).

‚ö° OCPU Calculation Example
Web Server (WordPress) ‚Üí 2 OCPU + 8GB RAM

Mail Server ‚Üí 1 OCPU + 4GB RAM

Extra Services (Monitoring / Proxy / Test) ‚Üí 1 OCPU + 4GB RAM

üëâ Ei 3 ta instance milaile total = 4 OCPU + 16GB RAM (Free Tier limit er moddhe).
Ar baki 8GB RAM future use er jonno thakbe.

‚ö° OCPU Use er Best Practice
WordPress / eCommerce site ‚Üí At least 2 OCPU dorkar smooth performance er jonno.

Mail server (Postfix/Dovecot + SMTP) ‚Üí 1 OCPU e handle hoy.

Database (MySQL/MariaDB) ‚Üí Web er sathe same instance e rakhle valo (extra latency kombe).

Monitoring / Backup / Automation ‚Üí 1 OCPU e lightweight VM chalano jabe.

üëâ Mane holo, Oracle Free Tier e total 4 OCPU free, tumi nijer priority onujayi divide korte paro.

