2Ô∏è‚É£ Virtual Host Fix
‡¶Ü‡¶™‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶∞ /etc/apache2/sites-available/mail.zovenax.com.conf ‡¶è‡¶Æ‡¶® ‡¶π‡¶§‡ßá ‡¶π‡¶¨‡ßá:

