mail._domainkey.zovenax.com zovenax.com:mail:/etc/opendkim/keys/zovenax.com/mail.private
SigningTable:

*@zovenax.com mail._domainkey.zovenax.com
Trusted Hosts:

127.0.0.1
localhost
zovenax.com
Publish public key in DNS as TXT.

Step 8: SPF & DMARC DNS Records
