Add line (example):

/dev/sdb   /mnt/data   ext4   defaults,nofail   0   2
Explanation:

defaults ‚Üí normal mount options

nofail ‚Üí ‡¶Ø‡¶¶‡¶ø volume missing ‡¶•‡¶æ‡¶ï‡ßá, system boot ‡¶π‡¶¨‡ßá

0 2 ‚Üí fsck check order

Save ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá exit ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßÅ‡¶®‡•§

5Ô∏è‚É£ Test fstab without reboot
