sudo apt install apache2 python3-certbot-apache -y
Cloudflare DNS plugin (‡¶Ø‡¶¶‡¶ø DNS-validated SSL ‡¶®‡¶ø‡¶§‡ßá ‡¶ö‡¶æ‡¶ì):

